<% content_for(:title, "Tenant Rights by State - Tulip") %>

<% content_for(:head) do %>
  <meta name="description" content="Know your rights as a renter. State-by-state guide to tenant protections, security deposits, eviction rules, and habitability standards for long-term stays across the United States.">
<% end %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-lavender-light to-lavender flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brown">Tenant Rights by State</h1>
        <p class="text-brown-light text-sm">Know your rights when staying 30+ days</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-brown-light mt-4 leading-relaxed">
      Staying somewhere for over a month? In most states, you may have tenant rights that protect you
      even without a traditional lease. This guide covers security deposits, notice periods, eviction
      protections, and habitability standards for every U.S. state.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- State Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <% @states.each do |state| %>
      <%= link_to tenant_right_path(state_slug: state["slug"]), class: "group cozy-card p-4 hover:shadow-cozy-lg hover:border-sage transition-all duration-200" do %>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brown group-hover:text-sage-dark transition-colors"><%= state["name"] %></h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-brown-light mt-1 line-clamp-2"><%= state["summary"] %></p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex items-center text-xs text-sage-dark font-medium">
          <span>View rights</span>
          <svg class="w-3 h-3 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <!-- Disclaimer -->
  <div class="mt-8 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-cream border border-taupe-light">
    <p class="text-xs text-brown-light leading-relaxed">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This information is provided as a general reference and does not constitute legal advice.
      Laws change frequently and may vary by municipality. For specific legal questions about your tenancy,
      consult a licensed attorney in the relevant state.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
